Template: debtrack/download
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Download updates by cron.
 Should updates be downloaded by cron automaticly?

Template: debtrack/mdst
Type: string
Default: debtrack
Description: Destination of debtrack mails.
 Specify mail adresses which should receive debtrack mails.

Template: debtrack/apt
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Use apt hooks?
 Should debtrack run after installing packages with apt automaticly?

Template: debtrack/report
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Report pending upgrades?
 Should debtrack run verbose and report upgrades via mail in it's cronjob?
